{
  "texts": [
    "The dataset includes 65,240 patients' chest radiographs, totaling around 2.5 million, that have been annotated for the presence of 14 chest radiographic findings.",
    "It has a labeler that can gather observations from free text radiological reports and use an uncertainty label to identify any uncertainties (https:// doi. org/ 10.",
    "48550/ arXiv. 1901.",
    "07031) [49].",
    "65,379 patients' X-ray scans are included in the 377,110 image MIMIC-CXR dataset."
  ]
}